defaultital. Across our core cities there is no equivalence which can ensure
default that
default transport maximises economic, socia
defaultl and environmental benefits – 
defaultCore Cities
default are operating under a structure that is heavily centralised to central government. Excluding recent cha
defaultnges to business rate local retention, which makes little difference in this respect, 
default 
default 95% of all tax raised in English Cities goes to national government.
